author: TMZ Staff
title: Waka Flocka Flame Found Not Guilty in 2014 Airport Gun Case
text:
Breaking News Waka Flocka Flame is off the hook for packing heat at the Atlanta Airport ... he was just found not guilty.
Flame was busted in 2014 for having a handgun in his carry-on bag ... but claimed he accidentally grabbed his fiancee's bag at home and brought it to the airport in a mix-up.
A jury reportedly agreed it was an accident and only took 30 minutes to acquit the rapper ... as reported by Page Six .
Still, he should probably double check his luggage every time he flies from now on.
